    %% Platform Dependencies
    CodeFlare -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]
    CodeFlare -.->|OpenShift only| RouteAPI[OpenShift Route API<br/>route.openshift.io/v1]

    %% Managed Resources
    CodeFlare -->|creates & manages| RayCluster[Ray Clusters<br/>Services, Routes,<br/>NetworkPolicies]
    CodeFlare -->|creates & manages| AppWrappers[AppWrappers<br/>Workload bundles]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| CodeFlare
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto deploy| CodeFlare
    Notebooks[Jupyter Notebooks] -.->|SDK integration| CodeFlare

    %% Ray Ecosystem
    RayCluster -->|distributed compute| RayHead[Ray Head Pod<br/>Dashboard + Client API]
    RayCluster --> RayWorkers[Ray Worker Pods]

